<p><a name="List_of_teachers" id="List_of_teachers"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Advaita_Vedanta&amp;action=edit&amp;section=24" title="Edit section: List of teachers">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">List of teachers</span></h2>
<div class="rellink noprint relarticle mainarticle">Main article: <a href="/wiki/List_of_teachers_of_Advaita_Vedanta" title="List of teachers of Advaita Vedanta">List of teachers of Advaita Vedanta</a></div>
<p>Advaita Vedanta has had many teachers over the centuries in <a href="/wiki/India" title="India">India</a> and other countries.</p>
